title: Rocket Lab's 'Hungry Hippo' Neutron fairing arrives at spaceport in Virginia
description: The "hungry hippo" fairing for Rocket Lab's new Neutron launch vehicle has arrived for integration at the company's Virginia Spaceport facilities.
